254
00:20:11,790 --> 00:20:13,150
♪ One day ♪

255
00:20:13,370 --> 00:20:15,820
♪ You will turn up gorgeously ♪

256
00:20:15,980 --> 00:20:17,950
♪ And hold my hands ♪

257
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:24,460
♪ To envisage our future ♪

258
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:27,400
[Next episode]

259
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:29,490
That's the scent of
a Grand Soul Land Master.

260
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:31,560
You won't be able to pass
the God of the Ocean's test

261
00:20:31,860 --> 00:20:33,090
for land soul masters.

262
00:20:33,260 --> 00:20:34,490
Devil White Sharks.

263
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:37,460
I've never heard of Shrek School.

264
00:20:37,700 --> 00:20:40,590
At least make up something convincing
if you're going to lie.

265
00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:42,960
Why do you reject everyone that comes?

266
00:20:43,130 --> 00:20:47,960
Only those who come before
the Seahorse Totem can take the test.

267
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:49,360
If you act rash while young,

268
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:50,760
you'll pay with your own life.

269
